0.2.0 - 2026-02-08

* New safer deletion behaviour, launch agents in the home directory
  are moved to the user's Trash whereas launch agents in the /Library
  folder are moved to the current working directory. '-d' argument
  can be used to override this behaviour and hard delete.
* Elevated permissions are only used when needed, no longer used on
  launch agents in the user's own Library folder.
* Launch agents to be deleted are printed with less formatting for
  easier scripting.
* New '-y' argument bypasses yes/no confirmation and produces less
  output, intended for cron jobs.
* New '-v' verbose argument prints more details to the terminal.
* New '-u' argument will search for launch agents only in the user's
  own Library folder.
* Makefile now uses 'install' command instead of 'mv' and 'chmod'
  combo.

0.1.0 - 2020-08-19

* Initial version with exclusion and confirmation before deletion.
* Makefile for install and uninstall included.